    "scene": "A depth-first spelunker paints visited caves; backtrack when dead ends hiss — addWord char-by-char; suggest = DFS collecting words under….",
    "acquired": "Trie spelunker: carve chars into caves; prefix walk then DFS harvest every word-flagged chamber till limit",
    "time": "O(word len) insert/lookup",
    "space": "O(total chars)",
    "code": "package main\ntype dictNode struct {\n\tchildren map[rune]*dictNode\n\tword     bool\n}\n\ntype dictionaryAndSpell struct {\n\troot *dictNode\n}\n\nfunc newDictionaryAndSpell(words []string) *dictionaryAndSpell {\n\td := &dictionaryAndSpell{root: &dictNode{children: map[rune]*dictNode{}}}\n\tfor _, w := range words {\n\t\td.addWord(w)\n\t}\n\treturn d\n}\n\nfunc (d *dictionaryAndSpell) addWord(word string) {\n\tnode := d.root\n\tfor _, ch := range word {\n\t\tif node.children[ch] == nil {\n\t\t\tnode.children[ch] = &dictNode{children: map[rune]*dictNode{}}\n\t\t}\n\t\tnode = node.children[ch]\n\t}\n\tnode.word = true\n}\n\nfunc (d *dictionaryAndSpell) search(word string) bool {\n\tnode := d.root\n\tfor _, ch := range word {\n\t\tif node.children[ch] == nil {\n\t\t\treturn false\n\t\t}\n\t\tnode = node.children[ch]\n\t}\n\treturn node.word\n}\n\nfunc (d *dictionaryAndSpell) suggest(prefix string, limit int) []string {\n\tnode := d.root\n\tfor _, ch := range prefix {\n\t\tif node.children[ch] == nil {\n\t\t\treturn nil\n\t\t}\n\t\tnode = node.children[ch]\n\t}\n\tvar out []string\n\tvar dfs func(n *dictNode, path string)\n\tdfs = func(n *dictNode, path string) {\n\t\tif len(out) >= limit {\n\t\t\treturn\n\t\t}\n\t\tif n.word {\n\t\t\tout = append(out, path)\n\t\t}\n\t\tfor ch, child := range n.children {\n\t\t\tdfs(child, path+string(ch))\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tdfs(node, prefix)\n\treturn out\n}\n",
    "notes": "# Notes: 16.1 Dictionary and spell\n\n## Status\n- [ ] First pass  [ ] Blind recall  [ ] Interview-ready\n\n\n## Scene\nRead the `--- Scene ---` block in [`solution.go`](./solution.go) before each recall.\n\n## Mistakes\n-\n\n## Revisions\n- YYYY-MM-DD:",
