    "title": "Find Kth largest in stream",
    "ask": "Find Kth largest in stream.",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "tags": [
      "design"
    ],
    "pattern": "Min-heap size k",
    "visual": "Min-heap of the k largest seen; its root is the kth largest",
    "memorize": "push val; if size>k popMin; answer is heap[0]",
    "scene": "Neon parrots in a pawn shop — one squawks each value, the other squawks what completes the deal — push val; if size>k popMin; answer is heap[0].",
    "acquired": "Min-heap of the k largest seen—push val; if size>k popMin; answer is heap[0]",
    "time": "O(n log k)",
    "space": "O(k)",
    "code": "package main\ntype kthHeap struct {\n\tvals []int\n}\n\nfunc (h *kthHeap) push(v int) {\n\th.vals = append(h.vals, v)\n\ti := len(h.vals) - 1\n\tfor i > 0 {\n\t\tp := (i - 1) / 2\n\t\tif h.vals[p] <= h.vals[i] {\n\t\t\tbreak\n\t\t}\n\t\th.vals[p], h.vals[i] = h.vals[i], h.vals[p]\n\t\ti = p\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc (h *kthHeap) popMin() int {\n\ttop := h.vals[0]\n\tlast := h.vals[len(h.vals)-1]\n\th.vals = h.vals[:len(h.vals)-1]\n\tif len(h.vals) == 0 {\n\t\treturn top\n\t}\n\th.vals[0] = last\n\ti := 0\n\tfor {\n\t\tl, r := 2*i+1, 2*i+2\n\t\tsmallest := i\n\t\tif l < len(h.vals) && h.vals[l] < h.vals[smallest] {\n\t\t\tsmallest = l\n\t\t}\n\t\tif r < len(h.vals) && h.vals[r] < h.vals[smallest] {\n\t\t\tsmallest = r\n\t\t}\n\t\tif smallest == i {\n\t\t\tbreak\n\t\t}\n\t\th.vals[i], h.vals[smallest] = h.vals[smallest], h.vals[i]\n\t\ti = smallest\n\t}\n\treturn top\n}\n\nfunc findKthLargestInStream(k int, nums []int) func(int) int {\n\th := &kthHeap{}\n\tfor _, v := range nums {\n\t\th.push(v)\n\t\tif len(h.vals) > k {\n\t\t\th.popMin()\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn func(v int) int {\n\t\th.push(v)\n\t\tif len(h.vals) > k {\n\t\t\th.popMin()\n\t\t}\n\t\treturn h.vals[0]\n\t}\n}\n",
    "notes": "# Notes: 15.6 Find Kth largest in stream\n\n## Status\n- [ ] First pass  [ ] Blind recall  [ ] Interview-ready\n\n\n## Scene\nRead the `--- Scene ---` block in [`solution.go`](./solution.go) before each recall.\n\n## Mistakes\n-\n\n## Revisions\n- YYYY-MM-DD:",
