    "pattern": "Two heaps median",
    "visual": "Max-heap holds the low half, min-heap the high half, kept balanced",
    "memorize": "push low, move its top to high, rebalance; median from the tops",
    "scene": "K sorted streams as screaming pipes — merge the loudest heads in a cursed priority queue — push low, move its top to high, rebalance; median from the….",
